      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl text-center font-bold tracking-tight !leading-normal mb-10 text-base-content">Pushing Changes Upstream</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 !font-light md:text-xl text-base-content">You can push your changes remotely by navigate to the extension's root folder, and use Git to push changes.
      Alternatively, use Bonfire's helpers like <code>just contrib</code> if you need to commit files that belong to multiple extensions or <code>just update-dep *dep*</code> for specific ones (e.g., <i>just update-dep bonfire_me</i>).</p>

      <p class="mt-5 !font-light md:text-xl text-base-content">You're now equipped to contribute to Bonfire extensions, enhancing the framework's capabilities. Your contributions are vital to the Bonfire community, and we encourage you to keep exploring and improving the project.</p>
